title: HELP BUG????
body:
So I just finished a 50 minute game getting s- and it didn't show the token thing congratulation me i got an s- with kindred??? Even though i am level 6??? Rito help me pls
http://prntscr.com/dp6mdp

replies.body: To get level 7 tokens you have to get S or S+ grades. S- grades only apply for the level 6 tokens.
